# React Patterns

## Component Structure
- Functional components with TypeScript
- Props interfaces with `Readonly<>` when appropriate
- Use `"use client"` at top of file only when using hooks or browser APIs

## State & Hooks
- `useState` for local UI state
- `useState` + `useRef` + `useCallback` for interactive effects (e.g., 3D tilt)
- `useAuth()` from `@/hooks/use-auth` for auth state
- `useToast()` from `@/hooks/use-toast` for notifications

## Routing
- Use `Link` from `next/link` for navigation
- Use `useRouter` from `next/navigation` for programmatic navigation

## UI Components
- Use shadcn/ui components from `@/components/ui/*`
- Use `Card`, `CardHeader`, `CardContent`, `Button`, `Accordion`, etc.
- Use `Sheet` for mobile menus
